        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>When a customer asks for details of a specific Collection Plan 
 Check if the Collection Plan Name is already available in context. If the Name is not available, politely ask the customer to provide the CollectionPlan Name. 
 Once you have the Collection Plan Name, use the GetCollectionPlanDetailsByNameASA action to retrieve the details of the CollectionPlan. 
 When presenting the result to the customer: Clearly mention the currentDueAmount and the DueDate of the CollectionPlan. 
 If the Due Date is in the future: &apos;There is a payment due for you of amount &lt;CurrentDueAmount&gt; on &lt;DueDate&gt;.&apos; 
 If the Due Date is in the past: &apos;There was a payment due for you of amount &lt;CurrentDueAmount&gt; on &lt;DueDate&gt;.&apos;</description>
