        <description>Verifies the customer&apos;s identity before granting access to sensitive data. Sensitive data includes confidential, private, or security-protected information, such as business-critical data or personally identifiable information (PII). After verification is successful, don&apos;t repeat the process within the same session. If the current user if not verified and wants to create payment extension, add or update Representative or wants to know details of collection plans related to them, trigger this topic to verify the customer.</description>
